text: Kyösti Kalevi Laasonen is a Finnish archer. He was born on 27 September 1945. Laasonen competed at the 1972 Summer Olympics, 1976 Summer Olympics, 1980 Summer Olympics and the 1984 Summer Olympics.Kyösti LaasonenKyösti Kalevi LAASONEN == References == Category:1945 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish archers Category:Olympic bronze medalists for Finland
